an#L119-L120","name":"AddCommSemigroup","docLink":"./Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.html#AddCommSemigroup","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.lean#L115-L117","name":"add_assoc","docLink":"./Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.html#add_assoc","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.lean#L112-L113","name":"AddSemigroup","docLink":"./Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.html#AddSemigroup","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.lean#L92-L94","name":"gpow_rec","docLink":"./Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.html#gpow_rec","doc":"The fundamental power operation in a group. `gpow_rec n a = a*a*...*a` n times, for integer `n`.\nUse instead `a ^ n`,  which has better definitional behavior. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.lean#L86-L88","name":"gsmul_rec","docLink":"./Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.html#gsmul_rec","doc":"The fundamental scalar multiplication in an additive group. `gsmul_rec n a = a+a+...+a` n\ntimes, for integer `n`. Use instead `n • a`, which has better definitional behavior. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.lean#L73-L75","name":"npow_rec","docLink":"./Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.html#npow_rec","doc":"The fundamental power operation in a monoid. `npow_rec n a = a*a*...*a` n times.\nUse instead `a ^ n`,  which has better definitional behavior. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.lean#L65-L67","name":"nsmul_rec","docLink":"./Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.html#nsmul_rec","doc":"The fundamental scalar multiplication in an additive monoid. `nsmul_rec n a = a+a+...+a` n\ntimes. Use instead `n • a`, which has better definitional behavior. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.lean#L50-L50","name":"«term_⁻¹»","docLink":"./Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.html#«term_⁻¹»","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.lean#L47-L48","name":"Inv","docLink":"./Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.html#Inv","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.lean#L43-L44","name":"One.ofOfNat1","docLink":"./Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.html#One.ofOfNat1","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.lean#L39-L40","name":"One.toOfNat1","docLink":"./Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.html#One.toOfNat1","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.lean#L35-L36","name":"One","docLink":"./Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.html#One","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.lean#L31-L32","name":"Zero.ofOfNat0","docLink":"./Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.html#Zero.ofOfNat0","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.lean#L28-L29","name":"Zero.toOfNat0","docLink":"./Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.html#Zero.toOfNat0","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Algebra/Group/Defs.lean#L25-L26","name":"Zero","doc